 not seem logical to me.<hr height=1 noshade id=quote></BLOCKQUOTE id=quote></font id=quote><font face="Verdana" size=2 id=quote><br /><br />Are you suggesting that we try to twitch every ****ed cleric in the CH chain at least once per minute?</span id="msg"></font><br><br></td>
